      • evaluateNoException

        public static int evaluateNoException(AST ast)
        Similar to evaluate, except an EvaluatorException triggers a test failure. This lifts the burden of annotating tests which are supposed to pass with the otherwise superfluous EvaluatorException.
        Parameters:
        ast - The AST to be evaluated
        Returns:
        The value of the expression after it is evaluated
